item.description:
When I first tried the pre-release of the upcoming tox rewrite, I noticed tox itself has funky new colors - which I like a lot&hellip;
But what happened with the green dots for pytest'soutput?
You may recall, running the old tox or pytest directly, the dots would be green&hellip;
why has this changed Honestly, I am not 100% sure.
But I know how to get the colors back.
All you need to do is changing this line commands = pytest {posargs} in your tox.
